270
00:21:47.041 --> 00:21:48.291
<i>I'm glad to hear your voice.</i>

271
00:21:50.625 --> 00:21:51.958
How do you have this number?

272
00:21:52.541 --> 00:21:53.541
Come on. Jim...

273
00:21:54.041 --> 00:21:55.458
I have friends everywhere.

274
00:21:56.541 --> 00:21:57.375
<i>You told me.</i>

275
00:21:57.458 --> 00:21:59.541
All calls are recorded here.

276
00:21:59.625 --> 00:22:00.750
<i>It wouldn't be funny if not.</i>

277
00:22:01.333 --> 00:22:02.875
Find your boy

278
00:22:03.916 --> 00:22:06.375
and tell him to give me back
what Nigel stole from me.

279
00:22:07.208 --> 00:22:09.000
<i>I don't know what you're talking about.</i>

280
00:22:10.083 --> 00:22:11.666
Jim. if he's still alive.

281
00:22:11.750 --> 00:22:14.875
It's just because we both know
that shouldn't be there.

282
00:22:16.333 --> 00:22:18.083
This call is courtesy.

283
00:22:20.166 --> 00:22:21.958
Nigel tried to stop us.

284
00:22:23.333 --> 00:22:24.791
Don't make the same mistake.

285
00:22:25.375 --> 00:22:28.375
-Listen to me...
<i>- Find your boy. Or I will.</i>

286
00:22:38.125 --> 00:22:41.083
{\an8}MI6 SAFE FLOOR

287
00:22:44.708 --> 00:22:46.208
If I tell you the truth.

288
00:22:47.125 --> 00:22:49.666
I thought it would be busted
after the trip.

289
00:22:50.333 --> 00:22:51.458
but I'm doing great.

290
00:22:51.541 --> 00:22:52.375
Be quiet.

291
00:22:53.833 --> 00:22:54.833
Come on. man...

292
00:22:56.208 --> 00:22:59.083
Greer told me it would be easy.
The same as you.

293
00:23:00.791 --> 00:23:04.875
In your new job they say:
"The guy is still a spy. How cool."

294
00:23:04.958 --> 00:23:06.833
- Know? It can happen.
- No.

295
00:23:07.750 --> 00:23:08.791
That never happens.

296
00:23:21.333 --> 00:23:22.333
This has indeed happened.

297
00:23:31.875 --> 00:23:33.041
Sit down.

298
00:23:35.291 --> 00:23:36.291
Who was it?

299
00:23:38.333 --> 00:23:41.750
We will find out
when the police examine the body.

300
00:23:42.666 --> 00:23:44.666
To your little friend. Mike November.

301
00:23:44.750 --> 00:23:46.541
They are looking for him in Dubrovnik.

302
00:23:46.625 --> 00:23:49.000
people look for it
That you could return the favor.

303
00:23:49.083 --> 00:23:51.500
I can send him there in an hour.

304
00:23:52.416 --> 00:23:55.625
And you. Jack Ryan.
I'm sure you're going to tell me that you're a civilian.

305
00:23:55.708 --> 00:23:57.375
- Because I am.
- Very good.

306
00:23:57.458 --> 00:23:59.166
Better for Emirati intelligence.

307
00:23:59.250 --> 00:24:01.333
You are a suspect in a double homicide.

308
00:24:01.416 --> 00:24:03.958
Oh really? It was you who shot.

309
00:24:04.541 --> 00:24:05.625
From what angle?

310
00:24:06.583 --> 00:24:08.041
you heard the shot

311
00:24:08.125 --> 00:24:10.125
and you saw me appear on the opposite side.

312
00:24:10.208 --> 00:24:11.416
Come on...

313
00:24:12.666 --> 00:24:14.083
I thought you were smarter.

314
00:24:14.166 --> 00:24:16.416
If you think you know me.
You will know that I have friends.

315
00:24:19.291 --> 00:24:21.000
The one in this photo?

316
00:24:21.916 --> 00:24:24.916
The one who has put your life in danger
instead of yours?

317
00:24:25.583 --> 00:24:27.958
And the one who killed a man in Karachi.

318
00:24:28.041 --> 00:24:29.458
Has he told you that story?

319
00:24:30.791 --> 00:24:33.833
I heard that Greer stabbed
to an asset that was going to kill him.

320
00:24:33.916 --> 00:24:36.291
but they demoted him
and they transferred him to Langley.

321
00:24:36.375 --> 00:24:37.958
Have you heard another version?

322
00:24:38.041 --> 00:24:39.916
- I don't think so.
- I imagined it.

323
00:24:40.416 --> 00:24:41.416
This...

324
00:24:42.916 --> 00:24:45.041
...is the man Greer killed.

325
00:24:45.625 --> 00:24:46.791
I don't see any stab wounds.

326
00:24:46.875 --> 00:24:48.625
The stabbings are scandalous.

327
00:24:48.708 --> 00:24:50.375
but a good torture

328
00:24:50.458 --> 00:24:51.625
It's pretty clean.

329
00:24:52.458 --> 00:24:56.375
Are you telling me that James Greer
tortured and killed this man?

330
00:24:56.458 --> 00:24:59.000
Not personally.
but he trained those who did.

331
00:25:00.416 --> 00:25:01.625
What do you know about Starling?

332
00:25:01.708 --> 00:25:02.875
-Starling?
- Yes.

333
00:25:03.625 --> 00:25:04.625
I think it's a bird.

334
00:25:05.375 --> 00:25:08.208
Because of your expression.
I see he hasn't told you anything.

335
00:25:10.250 --> 00:25:13.333
Greer and Nigel were chosen
to form a joint operation

336
00:25:13.416 --> 00:25:14.958
days after 9/11.

337
00:25:15.791 --> 00:25:18.458
A covert unit
created out of pure rage.

338
00:25:18.541 --> 00:25:22.375
Your rules. or lack thereof.
They reflected that feeling.

339
00:25:22.958 --> 00:25:25.583
They accumulated many deaths
the first days of the war.

340
00:25:25.666 --> 00:25:29.208
but then the advice
and committees became fashionable

341
00:25:29.291 --> 00:25:33.666
and. in Karachi. James Greer carried
with the blame for the entire program

342
00:25:33.750 --> 00:25:35.000
without revealing names.

343
00:25:36.083 --> 00:25:37.125
Names like Nigel.

344
00:25:37.708 --> 00:25:39.916
Like Crown. Liam Crown.

345
00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:41.583
- Did Greer mention it?
- No.

346
00:25:41.666 --> 00:25:42.666
Nothing?

347
00:25:44.958 --> 00:25:47.541
Last night I just had to pick up
a delivery from Nigel.

348
00:25:47.625 --> 00:25:48.791
but he didn't give me anything.

349
00:25:48.875 --> 00:25:49.791
I had nothing.

350
00:25:49.875 --> 00:25:51.333
Last night was a meeting.

351
00:25:51.416 --> 00:25:54.000
If Nigel knew something.
he would have only told Greer.

352
00:25:55.083 --> 00:25:56.875
So. I don't know what I can contribute.

353
00:25:57.458 --> 00:25:58.458
Answers.

354
00:25:59.000 --> 00:26:01.625
I wanted them from Nigel.
Now I want them from Greer.

355
00:26:01.708 --> 00:26:04.291
You've proven that I don't work for Greer.

356
00:26:04.375 --> 00:26:05.791
You are absolutely right.

357
00:26:07.291 --> 00:26:10.708
If you don't want things
things continue to go badly for you in Dubai.

358
00:26:11.875 --> 00:26:12.875
works for me.

359
00:26:19.083 --> 00:26:21.250
Are you really going to make me go alone?

360
00:26:21.333 --> 00:26:23.833
You don't need me
to dazzle some politicians.

361
00:26:27.458 --> 00:26:28.458
Jack.

362
00:26:29.750 --> 00:26:31.750
God. What the hell is happening?

363
00:26:34.666 --> 00:26:38.250
{\an8}RAF ALCONBURY
CAMBRIDGESHIRE. UNITED KINGDOM

364
00:26:56.333 --> 00:26:57.333
Wait.

365
00:26:58.083 --> 00:26:59.041
Emma.

366
00:26:59.125 --> 00:27:00.333
Andrew.

367
00:27:00.416 --> 00:27:02.500
Won't you introduce me to your new friends?

368
00:27:02.583 --> 00:27:05.041
- I don't know if I would call them...
- You're right.

369
00:27:05.708 --> 00:27:09.083
Let's see if I don't have to arrest you
before we get intimate.

370
00:27:09.166 --> 00:27:10.208
Come on?

371
00:27:28.625 --> 00:27:30.625
Where the hell were you?

372
00:27:30.708 --> 00:27:31.708
In Dubai.

373
00:27:32.583 --> 00:27:35.791
I thought it was clear.
Sorry if it was difficult for you to locate me.

374
00:27:35.875 --> 00:27:37.041
And shit.

375
00:27:37.958 --> 00:27:40.000
You have worked with Nigel
behind our backs.

376
00:27:40.083 --> 00:27:41.083
On the contrary.

377
00:27:41.583 --> 00:27:43.250
Nigel didn't know I was following him.

378
00:27:45.458 --> 00:27:47.083
Did you doubt his intentions?

379
00:27:47.666 --> 00:27:48.958
Not his intentions.

380
00:27:51.333 --> 00:27:52.416
Of your safety.

381
00:27:54.583 --> 00:27:57.875
Marlow. we face
to an international incident.

382
00:27:57.958 --> 00:27:59.250
He was a decorated agent.

383
00:27:59.333 --> 00:28:00.958
And he won't be the last dead.

384
00:28:02.041 --> 00:28:03.416
What do you know about his murderer?

385
00:28:04.166 --> 00:28:07.708
- How do you know we have something?
- Because. if not. I would be handcuffed.

386
00:28:08.833 --> 00:28:10.625
You need me to analyze it.

387
00:28:10.708 --> 00:28:11.916
All this.

388
00:28:12.833 --> 00:28:15.833
And this analysis depends
of the two Americans behind?

389
00:28:15.916 --> 00:28:17.041
From one of them.

390
00:28:17.541 --> 00:28:20.625
Nigel was due to meet
with Deputy Chief Greer on that boat.

391
00:28:21.375 --> 00:28:24.833
Now that he is dead. Greer is
the only one who has information about Starling.

392
00:28:26.750 --> 00:28:27.875
What the hell is Starling?

393
00:28:29.583 --> 00:28:30.958
Ask Greer.

394
00:28:31.041 --> 00:28:34.583
Do you expect me to get information from him?
to the deputy director of the CIA?

395
00:28:34.666 --> 00:28:35.666
No.

396
00:28:36.375 --> 00:28:37.375
Not you.

397
00:28:58.541 --> 00:29:01.500
{\an8}MI6 HEADQUARTERS
LONDON

398
00:29:08.875 --> 00:29:11.583
Marlow. will you accompany
Dr. Ryan to the boardroom

399
00:29:11.666 --> 00:29:13.083
to see the deputy director?

400
00:29:14.125 --> 00:29:15.125
Here.

401
00:29:16.041 --> 00:29:17.958
And you. Mr. November?

402
00:29:23.208 --> 00:29:24.750
Okay. Is the coffee good?

403
00:29:29.208 --> 00:29:31.291
Listen. I know how you feel.

404
00:29:31.375 --> 00:29:33.500
- You have no idea.
- But remember:

405
00:29:34.083 --> 00:29:36.458
Without Greer we have nothing.

406
00:29:42.250 --> 00:29:43.666
Jack. listen.

407
00:29:44.916 --> 00:29:46.416
I'm sorry for what happened.

408
00:29:46.500 --> 00:29:48.000
I think you know me and...

409
00:29:48.083 --> 00:29:51.291
From what I've heard.
It's clear that I don't know you at all.

410
00:29:51.375 --> 00:29:53.375
Has Agent Marlow informed you?

411
00:29:53.458 --> 00:29:55.541
About what? Starling?

412
00:29:56.625 --> 00:29:59.375
No. Just like you. Nigel kept it from him.

413
00:29:59.458 --> 00:30:01.000
To protect her.

414
00:30:01.083 --> 00:30:02.083
And me?

415
00:30:03.000 --> 00:30:06.125
Didn't you tell me shit
of what was happening there

416
00:30:06.208 --> 00:30:07.833
to protect me too?

417
00:30:08.458 --> 00:30:09.875
What was she doing in Dubai?

418
00:30:09.958 --> 00:30:11.916
I'd be worried about Nigel.

419
00:30:12.000 --> 00:30:15.000
That's where I get lost.
Why would I be worried?

420
00:30:21.875 --> 00:30:23.375
I received it 24 hours ago.

421
00:30:25.166 --> 00:30:26.041
Who are they?

422
00:30:26.750 --> 00:30:28.625
Mark Whitaker and Tobias Wilks.

423
00:30:28.708 --> 00:30:30.416
Fuck. I know Whitaker. he was...

424
00:30:30.500 --> 00:30:31.500
Former CIA agent.

425
00:30:32.083 --> 00:30:33.750
Wilks of MI6.

426
00:30:34.333 --> 00:30:35.833
How do you know that?

427
00:30:35.916 --> 00:30:38.458
- Nigel was in charge of both.
- Starling closed.

428
00:30:38.541 --> 00:30:40.750
- That's how it is. I closed it.
- When?

429
00:30:40.833 --> 00:30:43.000
Of course. just before we met.

430
00:30:44.041 --> 00:30:46.166
When you were demoted
for stabbing a guy.

431
00:30:46.250 --> 00:30:47.708
Is that what happened?

432
00:30:47.791 --> 00:30:49.291
I told you I closed it.

433
00:30:50.125 --> 00:30:51.666
two years ago.

434
00:30:51.750 --> 00:30:56.041
Wilks went to Nigel when he recruited him
a secret military contractor.

435
00:30:56.125 --> 00:30:57.333
Let's see if I guess: Crown.

436
00:30:57.916 --> 00:30:58.958
One year later.

437
00:31:00.000 --> 00:31:02.625
when Wilks realized
where did it come from...

438
00:31:02.708 --> 00:31:04.750
On a black ops team

439
00:31:04.833 --> 00:31:08.291
designed for psychological warfare.
murder

440
00:31:08.375 --> 00:31:10.875
and arm and train terrorist groups

441
00:31:10.958 --> 00:31:12.000
to eliminate others.

442
00:31:12.083 --> 00:31:14.958
breaking the rules
and ignoring the consequences?

443
00:31:15.041 --> 00:31:18.458
When he realized.
Wilks contacted a former agent.

444
00:31:18.541 --> 00:31:20.750
Nigel must have been
the most popular in the class.

445
00:31:20.833 --> 00:31:21.958
Nigel contacted me

446
00:31:22.041 --> 00:31:24.750
<i>to let me know that Crown
Starling had been resurrected.</i>

447
00:31:24.833 --> 00:31:26.958
<i>Of what they did. Of what they had done.</i>

448
00:31:28.250 --> 00:31:31.708
<i>He knew he couldn't
stop Crown right away.</i>

449
00:31:31.791 --> 00:31:34.041
- so he did the only thing he could.
- That?

450
00:31:34.625 --> 00:31:37.000
- Keep an eye on them.
- Until Crown found out.

451
00:31:38.333 --> 00:31:39.166
I didn't know it.

452
00:31:39.250 --> 00:31:41.541
- That was when you sent me. right?
- I didn't know.

453
00:31:41.625 --> 00:31:42.708
- To a civilian.
- I didn't know.

454
00:31:42.791 --> 00:31:43.708
To Dubai.

455
00:31:44.250 --> 00:31:46.333
When they discovered two agents.

456
00:31:46.416 --> 00:31:48.000
When they were killed...

457
00:31:48.083 --> 00:31:49.750
- No...
- ...for cleaning up the mess...

458
00:31:49.833 --> 00:31:51.875
- Grow up. damn it!
- ...that you left 20 years ago!

459
00:31:51.958 --> 00:31:53.000
Civil. my balls!

460
00:31:53.083 --> 00:31:57.083
Don't come to me with that fucking suit
acting as a stockbroker

461
00:31:57.166 --> 00:31:59.083
with everything you've seen and done.

462
00:32:00.708 --> 00:32:02.541
It is a shame for you and your country.

463
00:32:02.625 --> 00:32:04.625
- Is that what it's about?
- What do you think?

464
00:32:05.208 --> 00:32:08.708
Get away from the darkness
It is not the same as approaching the light.

465
00:32:09.208 --> 00:32:12.166
So save the moralistic lecture.

466
00:32:12.250 --> 00:32:14.083
- I don't give sermons.
- Of course.

467
00:32:14.166 --> 00:32:15.875
You have it written on your forehead.

468
00:32:15.958 --> 00:32:19.000
It was the first thing I have seen
as soon as you entered.

469
00:32:19.083 --> 00:32:20.833
The answers slip away from you.

470
00:32:20.916 --> 00:32:24.250
You've only come to read me the fucking primer.

471
00:32:25.041 --> 00:32:27.625
20 years ago
There was nothing but darkness.

472
00:32:27.708 --> 00:32:31.666
For every minute we lost
With the paperwork. a monster escaped.

473
00:32:32.375 --> 00:32:36.291
Starling was born out of common sense. dammit.

474
00:32:37.625 --> 00:32:39.041
If you are attacked. the rules change.

475
00:32:39.125 --> 00:32:40.583
And what do they exist for?

476
00:32:40.666 --> 00:32:43.541
With every blow.
With every death. we save lives!

477
00:32:47.541 --> 00:32:49.416
What had a price? Clear.

478
00:32:49.500 --> 00:32:51.291
It had a price.

479
00:32:53.875 --> 00:32:57.041
And only in a period of peace.
achieved at that price.

480
00:32:57.125 --> 00:32:58.708
You can pretend you didn't have it.

481
00:32:59.291 --> 00:33:00.458
Do you think so?

482
00:33:01.291 --> 00:33:03.500
I'm not aware of that price?

483
00:33:03.583 --> 00:33:05.041
I pay for it myself.

484
00:33:05.125 --> 00:33:08.208
Every night I come back
to an empty house. with no one.

485
00:33:08.291 --> 00:33:10.125
and every day that I wake up

486
00:33:10.208 --> 00:33:13.166
and I see that dream
that I was charged with defending

487
00:33:13.250 --> 00:33:14.583
maybe it doesn't even exist!

488
00:33:14.666 --> 00:33:17.333
Well muster up the fucking courage
to defend it as well.

489
00:33:17.833 --> 00:33:21.291
Because there are people killing monsters
so you don't have to.

490
00:33:22.125 --> 00:33:24.333
They keep the doors closed by hand.

491
00:33:26.500 --> 00:33:28.583
Smart. dangerous people.

492
00:33:29.666 --> 00:33:31.875
And if you tell them that their sacrifice

493
00:33:31.958 --> 00:33:34.500
has not met your expectations.

494
00:33:34.583 --> 00:33:35.958
that they are the monsters.

495
00:33:36.041 --> 00:33:37.708
maybe some will regret it.

496
00:33:37.791 --> 00:33:41.708
but others will show you what happens
when the doors open wide.

497
00:33:43.333 --> 00:33:45.458
What differentiates you from him?

498
00:33:51.708 --> 00:33:52.708
Don't know.

499
00:33:55.166 --> 00:33:56.291
Maybe nothing.

500
00:33:59.000 --> 00:34:00.583
Or maybe you.

501
00:34:02.291 --> 00:34:05.291
You and your fucking moral compass.

502
00:34:05.375 --> 00:34:09.916
You and your unwavering conviction
about what is right and what is wrong.

503
00:34:12.208 --> 00:34:13.416
Maybe I'm envious of you.

504
00:34:17.208 --> 00:34:18.833
Or maybe I'm wrong.

505
00:34:20.375 --> 00:34:22.583
But in the middle lies the truth.

506
00:34:23.291 --> 00:34:25.666
And if you don't know how to accept
what that truth implies.

507
00:34:25.750 --> 00:34:28.375
I guess...

508
00:34:29.875 --> 00:34:31.750
...yes you're just a fucking analyst.

509
00:34:45.666 --> 00:34:47.250
Let's get started.

510
00:34:48.416 --> 00:34:52.541
Doctor Ryan. I understand
who no longer works for the CIA.

511
00:34:52.625 --> 00:34:54.625
I understood that too.

512
00:34:55.375 --> 00:34:56.208
And now?

513
00:34:56.291 --> 00:34:57.333
He is a collaborator.

514
00:34:58.791 --> 00:34:59.625
Understood.

515
00:35:01.333 --> 00:35:04.791
Doctor Ryan. Agent Marlow
He assures that he did not recover anything

516
00:35:04.875 --> 00:35:08.416
during his meeting with Nigel Cooke.

517
00:35:08.500 --> 00:35:10.333
That's how it is.

518
00:35:11.375 --> 00:35:12.208
Already.

519
00:35:12.291 --> 00:35:15.916
Well. thanks to the cooperation
of SIGINT in Dubai.

520
00:35:16.000 --> 00:35:20.208
we have discovered a hard drive
of Nigel's murderer. Yusef Bajwa.

521
00:35:21.000 --> 00:35:23.291
Information for Deputy Chief Greer.

522
00:35:23.375 --> 00:35:24.458
It was damaged.

523
00:35:24.541 --> 00:35:26.500
but Claudia has recovered something.

524
00:35:26.583 --> 00:35:27.500
Claudia?

525
00:35:27.583 --> 00:35:30.708
As Deputy Director Spear says.
was damaged by water.

526
00:35:30.791 --> 00:35:34.750
but we have been able to discover the following.

527
00:35:35.458 --> 00:35:36.625
What's that?

528
00:35:36.708 --> 00:35:39.750
They are images
of the Karakoram mountain range.

529
00:35:39.833 --> 00:35:40.708
east of Kabul.

530
00:35:40.791 --> 00:35:43.416
spreads
to northern Pakistan and China.

531
00:35:44.500 --> 00:35:45.958
However. the annex...

532
00:35:46.750 --> 00:35:48.750
- Is that London?
- Yes sir.

533
00:35:48.833 --> 00:35:51.458
The other file appears to be
from a more recent operation.

534
00:35:51.541 --> 00:35:55.458
Includes photographs. coded diagrams
and bank statements.

535
00:35:57.375 --> 00:35:58.541
The last transaction?

536
00:35:59.583 --> 00:36:00.666
A retreat.

537
00:36:00.750 --> 00:36:03.083
It was four days ago

538
00:36:03.166 --> 00:36:05.833
at an ATM on the corner of Middlesex
with Harrow Place.

539
00:36:07.333 --> 00:36:08.333
Aldgate.

540
00:36:10.708 --> 00:36:12.166
How do you possibly know that?

541
00:36:12.250 --> 00:36:14.125
Because I know this plan.

542
00:36:15.208 --> 00:36:17.541
I stopped him. 20 years ago.

543
00:36:19.500 --> 00:36:21.958
The coup was masterminded by the PMN.

544
00:36:22.708 --> 00:36:25.791
a radicalized military group
which we accessed with Starling.

545
00:36:25.875 --> 00:36:26.916
With what objective?

546
00:36:27.666 --> 00:36:29.166
Blow up Tower Bridge.

547
00:36:29.750 --> 00:36:33.375
{\an8}CIA HEADQUARTERS
MANAGEMENT OFFICE

548
00:36:34.500 --> 00:36:36.833
- Greer?
- Elizabeth. we have a problem.

549
00:36:36.916 --> 00:36:39.291
<i>- What is it about?</i>
- You must come to London.

550
00:36:40.416 --> 00:36:41.750
Good. Thank you all.

551
00:36:41.833 --> 00:36:44.708
I recommend that they close the bridge
immediately.

552
00:36:44.791 --> 00:36:46.666
Excuse me. Based on what?

553
00:36:46.750 --> 00:36:49.833
Incomplete information
about a blow that has already stopped?

554
00:36:49.916 --> 00:36:52.666
Nigel has died because of this.
He knew I would understand.

555
00:36:52.750 --> 00:36:53.916
And what does it mean?

556
00:36:54.500 --> 00:36:56.458
That they have resurrected Starling.

557
00:36:58.833 --> 00:37:00.000
Who has resurrected him?

558
00:37:00.791 --> 00:37:02.000
Liam Crown.

559
00:37:02.083 --> 00:37:03.125
Liam Crown?

560
00:37:05.291 --> 00:37:07.083
The national hero. decorated

561
00:37:07.708 --> 00:37:09.875
- with the Victoria Cross?
- We were going to get to that.

562
00:37:11.083 --> 00:37:12.583
I'd say we're already there!

563
00:37:25.125 --> 00:37:26.666
Tell me what you know about Crown.

564
00:37:26.750 --> 00:37:28.583
<i>Elizabeth. for your protection...</i>

565
00:37:28.666 --> 00:37:31.250
In case you forgot.
It's not me who needs protection.

566
00:37:32.166 --> 00:37:35.125
I met Crown and Nigel
on the way to Karachi.

567
00:37:36.041 --> 00:37:38.833
<i>We followed the trail
of the Pakistani Militant Nexus.</i>

568
00:37:38.916 --> 00:37:42.125
<i>The PMN planned attacks all over the world.</i>

569
00:37:42.208 --> 00:37:44.833
- but his main objective was London.
- Come on.

570
00:37:45.708 --> 00:37:47.416
Our methods were brutal.

571
00:37:48.083 --> 00:37:50.541
<i>Sometimes we only took poison out of them.</i>

572
00:37:51.125 --> 00:37:54.250
<i>A confession led us
to the richest neighborhood in Karachi.</i>

573
00:38:06.833 --> 00:38:09.875
<i>Crown managed to capture
to a living PMN member:</i>

574
00:38:11.833 --> 00:38:14.625
<i>the deputy chief of staff
of the Pakistani Army.</i>

575
00:38:17.291 --> 00:38:21.083
<i>My job was to interrogate him.</i>

576
00:38:22.250 --> 00:38:25.750
<i>What he told us
He led us to a safe house in Aldgate.</i>

577
00:38:26.916 --> 00:38:27.916
COINCIDENCE

578
00:38:28.000 --> 00:38:31.250
<i>We stopped the attack
three hours before it happened.</i>

579
00:38:31.333 --> 00:38:32.166
FIXED COORDINATES

580
00:38:32.250 --> 00:38:33.583
And the one you questioned?

581
00:38:34.291 --> 00:38:38.083
He suffered a heart attack
while we got the information out of him.

582
00:38:38.166 --> 00:38:39.500
And they blamed you.

583
00:38:39.583 --> 00:38:40.416
<i>Yes.</i>

584
00:38:40.500 --> 00:38:42.666
<i>Is that when Starling closed?</i>

585
00:38:42.750 --> 00:38:43.875
We believed that.

586
00:38:45.291 --> 00:38:48.708
Nigel discovered that Crown was still in charge
of Starling operations.

587
00:38:49.291 --> 00:38:51.458
God. So that?

588
00:38:52.125 --> 00:38:55.958
Crown is the kind of soldier who thinks
that we can never protect ourselves

589
00:38:56.041 --> 00:38:57.333
with politics and diplomacy.

590
00:38:58.375 --> 00:38:59.708
<i>And after 9/11.</i>

591
00:38:59.791 --> 00:39:02.541
learned that the only way
to change things

592
00:39:02.625 --> 00:39:04.708
It's doing what no one else wants to do.

593
00:39:05.291 --> 00:39:07.041
<i>And why expose ourselves?</i>

594
00:39:07.125 --> 00:39:09.666
<i>Because now he feels betrayed.</i>

595
00:39:10.583 --> 00:39:12.333
<i>We try to put an end to it.</i>

596
00:39:12.416 --> 00:39:13.333
<i>It's a message.</i>

597
00:39:15.041 --> 00:39:19.000
<i>He wants us to know what he is going to do
just what we taught him.</i>

598
00:39:20.291 --> 00:39:21.291
<i>And what is it?</i>

599
00:39:22.750 --> 00:39:23.750
Whatever it takes.

600
00:39:35.666 --> 00:39:37.125
I hope it's worth it.

601
00:39:37.208 --> 00:39:40.666
Nigel risked everything by going there alone
to achieve this.

602
00:39:43.458 --> 00:39:44.958
Emma. I'm so sorry...

603
00:39:45.041 --> 00:39:47.000
Were you serious about what you said?

604
00:39:48.166 --> 00:39:49.291
What did I say?

605
00:39:51.458 --> 00:39:54.333
That the dream you defended
maybe it doesn't even exist.

606
00:39:58.458 --> 00:39:59.625
God...

607
00:39:59.708 --> 00:40:02.083
I didn't know that MI6 was tapping into their rooms.

608
00:40:02.166 --> 00:40:03.625
That would be unethical.

609
00:40:04.916 --> 00:40:06.041
I put it in your jacket.

610
00:40:07.625 --> 00:40:08.625
When?

611
00:40:10.666 --> 00:40:11.958
A lady does not reveal her secrets.

612
00:40:13.875 --> 00:40:15.083
Nigel was sold.

613
00:40:15.166 --> 00:40:17.583
I had to make sure
that Greer did not work with Crown.

614
00:40:18.250 --> 00:40:20.000
Discover more things about you...

615
00:40:21.208 --> 00:40:22.833
...has been a plus.

616
00:40:23.416 --> 00:40:25.833
You don't make it easy for me to trust you.

617
00:40:25.916 --> 00:40:27.083
I make it impossible for you.

618
00:40:28.291 --> 00:40:30.416
Unless our loyalties coincide.

619
00:40:35.583 --> 00:40:37.666
And what do my dreams matter to you?

620
00:40:39.416 --> 00:40:40.541
They look familiar to me.

621
00:40:42.625 --> 00:40:44.250
<i>Are you watching this</i>

622
00:40:44.333 --> 00:40:46.666
<i>or is that camera shit?</i>

623
00:40:55.291 --> 00:40:57.166
<i>Good. Don't lose it.</i>

624
00:40:57.250 --> 00:40:58.250
Yes.

625
00:41:04.333 --> 00:41:05.333
As usual.

626
00:41:22.041 --> 00:41:23.375
Welcome. colonel.

627
00:41:23.458 --> 00:41:25.541
Or. rather. director.

628
00:41:25.625 --> 00:41:28.083
You've come a long way from CENTCOM.

629
00:41:28.166 --> 00:41:29.416
Yes. and you too.

630
00:41:30.458 --> 00:41:32.041
But I miss him every day.

631
00:41:33.291 --> 00:41:34.125
I'm glad to see you.

632
00:41:34.791 --> 00:41:35.791
Elizabeth.

633
00:41:38.791 --> 00:41:39.916
Thanks for coming.

634
00:41:40.625 --> 00:41:41.958
I know that the circumstances...

635
00:41:42.041 --> 00:41:44.583
You did your job. James.
Don't apologize.

636
00:41:45.625 --> 00:41:47.458
And for you? Always.

637
00:42:12.458 --> 00:42:13.500
Come on.

638
00:42:14.208 --> 00:42:15.375
Green light!

639
00:43:34.000 --> 00:43:34.833
Get inside.

640
00:43:47.958 --> 00:43:49.625
- Boss.
- Director.

641
00:43:50.208 --> 00:43:52.083
Thank you for receiving us so quickly.

642
00:43:52.166 --> 00:43:53.000
Of course.

643
00:43:53.666 --> 00:43:55.750
- Deputy Director Greer.
- Boss.

644
00:43:57.333 --> 00:43:58.500
This way. please.

645
00:44:05.333 --> 00:44:06.416
Fuck!

646
00:44:27.166 --> 00:44:28.000
Come on!

647
00:44:28.083 --> 00:44:31.041
- Armed police!
- Come on!

648
00:44:32.541 --> 00:44:33.541
Armed police!

649
00:44:34.208 --> 00:44:37.250
I don't know about you.
But. even with experience.

650
00:44:37.333 --> 00:44:40.750
it's hard for me to express
the weight of these situations.

651
00:44:40.833 --> 00:44:41.666
Fast!

652
00:44:41.750 --> 00:44:45.791
<i>That a person can have
such an immovable perspective

653
00:44:46.500 --> 00:44:49.583
who believes that in the world
only darkness remains...

654
00:44:51.625 --> 00:44:55.791
<i>...and come to the conclusion
that there is no more light left to fight for.</i>

655
00:44:56.500 --> 00:44:57.333
Damn.

656
00:44:59.750 --> 00:45:00.958
We have the suspect.

657
00:45:01.666 --> 00:45:04.791
Well. we have to bring it here now.
Don't you think?

658
00:45:07.875 --> 00:45:11.250
<i>We trust that our soldiers
with a spear

659
00:45:12.250 --> 00:45:13.500
<i>pierce the darkness.</i>

660
00:45:15.541 --> 00:45:17.291
As a soldier. this man...

661
00:45:19.250 --> 00:45:21.166
...is the tip of that spear.

662
00:45:23.833 --> 00:45:24.916
And as a mentor.

663
00:45:27.416 --> 00:45:29.000
my guarantor of hope.

664
00:45:40.041 --> 00:45:41.083
Say.

665
00:45:41.166 --> 00:45:42.041
Jack. what do you have?

666
00:45:42.125 --> 00:45:43.750
Just what you said.

667
00:45:44.500 --> 00:45:46.833
The only thing missing is a model of the bridge.

668
00:45:46.916 --> 00:45:48.791
There are explosives to blow up the foundations.

669
00:45:48.875 --> 00:45:49.875
I shit the bitch.

670
00:45:50.458 --> 00:45:51.291
Have you talked to him?

671
00:45:51.375 --> 00:45:53.583
He's saying it's not his.

672
00:45:53.666 --> 00:45:55.958
Those assholes never learn.

673
00:45:56.041 --> 00:45:57.041
He is a messenger.

674
00:45:57.750 --> 00:45:59.875
He was paid to accept a package.

675
00:45:59.958 --> 00:46:02.041
<i>- Did someone send you the equipment?</i>
- And shit.

676
00:46:03.333 --> 00:46:06.541
The scientist is recording this.
It is impossible for him to act alone.

677
00:46:06.625 --> 00:46:09.416
Maybe what he says is bullshit.
but everything fits.

678
00:46:09.500 --> 00:46:12.500
The meeting is over.
I'm taking Wright to the embassy.

679
00:46:13.083 --> 00:46:14.083
I'm going to go with him.

680
00:46:14.916 --> 00:46:15.916
Is it Jack?

681
00:46:16.833 --> 00:46:19.166
If it's him. you're not going to take me
nowhere.

682
00:46:19.875 --> 00:46:23.541
The information is good. but it doesn't add up.

683
00:46:24.166 --> 00:46:25.875
And why leave it sold?

684
00:46:26.500 --> 00:46:29.625
Do they leave him alone with so much material?
It doesn't make sense.

685
00:46:29.708 --> 00:46:32.458
Come on. Jack.
I'm risking more than my neck.

686
00:46:32.541 --> 00:46:34.875
<i>- Come in and get me something.</i>
- Holy shit.

687
00:46:34.958 --> 00:46:36.125
That?

688
00:46:36.208 --> 00:46:37.708
<i>"Sold."</i>

689
00:46:37.791 --> 00:46:39.833
- Where are you?
<i>- Why? What's happening?</i>

690
00:46:39.916 --> 00:46:40.750
God...

691
00:46:42.208 --> 00:46:44.041
What if Crown has set us up?

692
00:46:44.625 --> 00:46:47.291
What if it has made us look away?

693
00:46:47.875 --> 00:46:49.208
Look away from what?

694
00:46:51.083 --> 00:46:51.916
Of you.

695
00:46:59.375 --> 00:47:00.708
Elizabeth!

696
00:47:13.625 --> 00:47:14.625
Greer!

697
00:47:29.583 --> 00:47:30.833
- It has fallen.
- That?

698
00:47:30.916 --> 00:47:32.000
Greer is down!

699
00:47:32.083 --> 00:47:33.083
Shit.

700
00:47:51.250 --> 00:47:54.041
Agent 20JL here.

701
00:47:54.125 --> 00:47:56.250
We head southwest.
towards Leadenhall.

702
00:47:56.333 --> 00:47:58.250
Estimated time: less than ten minutes.

703
00:47:58.333 --> 00:48:01.166
<i>Roger. Agent Marlow.
Obtaining coordinates.</i>

704
00:49:02.958 --> 00:49:05.541
Get out of the way! Get out of the way. damn it!

705
00:49:26.708 --> 00:49:27.958
Come on. answer.

706
00:49:28.041 --> 00:49:29.208
Shit.

707
00:49:31.833 --> 00:49:32.666
Come on!

708
00:50:09.916 --> 00:50:13.166
<i>- Chase towards Horse Guards.</i>
- Turn left.

709
00:50:32.375 --> 00:50:34.500
Go through the tunnel. Come on!

710
00:50:39.500 --> 00:50:40.500
Do you have the key?

711
00:51:13.166 --> 00:51:14.125
Jack!

712
00:51:46.166 --> 00:51:47.666
Son of a bitch.

713
00:52:33.500 --> 00:52:34.458
Remove.

714
00:52:37.583 --> 00:52:38.416
Crown!

715
00:52:39.625 --> 00:52:40.625
Crown!

716
00:52:41.416 --> 00:52:42.250
Turn around!

717
00:53:26.750 --> 00:53:27.666
Fuck!

718
00:54:08.750 --> 00:54:09.750
Are you OK?

719
00:54:12.000 --> 00:54:14.708
Look at me. Are you OK? Are you hurt?

720
00:54:16.416 --> 00:54:17.500
He has died.

721
00:54:17.583 --> 00:54:18.666
Who?

722
00:54:18.750 --> 00:54:19.750
Wright.

723
00:54:20.625 --> 00:54:21.625
He has died.

724
00:54:23.583 --> 00:54:25.500
They cover us. The local is on the way.

725
00:54:25.583 --> 00:54:27.000
- We must take him.
- For.

726
00:54:27.083 --> 00:54:29.750
He is the acting director of the CIA
and they try to kill him.

727
00:54:29.833 --> 00:54:31.375
It has to disappear. Above.

728
00:54:31.458 --> 00:54:33.375
- We must go. Come on!
- Come on.

729
00:54:34.125 --> 00:54:34.958
Fast!

730
00:55:09.208 --> 00:55:10.208
High.

731
00:55:13.208 --> 00:55:14.208
Put it down.

732
00:55:33.791 --> 00:55:34.791
<i>Yes. sir.</i>

733
00:55:36.416 --> 00:55:37.291
<i>I understand.</i>

734
00:55:39.333 --> 00:55:40.333
Thank you. sir.

735
00:55:51.625 --> 00:55:53.000
When do they want you to come back?

736
00:55:55.083 --> 00:55:58.333
If you think I'm going to leave
after what he's done...

737
00:55:58.416 --> 00:55:59.500
You couldn't do anything.

738
00:56:00.958 --> 00:56:02.041
You know that. right?

739
00:56:03.000 --> 00:56:04.333
You couldn't know it.

740
00:56:05.583 --> 00:56:06.583
She was the light.

741
00:56:09.875 --> 00:56:11.208
In the dark.

742
00:56:11.958 --> 00:56:13.041
she was the light.

743
00:56:16.333 --> 00:56:17.333
It was.

744
00:56:20.166 --> 00:56:21.083
I'm ready.

745
00:56:22.625 --> 00:56:23.625
Whenever you want.

746
00:56:29.916 --> 00:56:33.375
We can't trust anyone.
neither inside nor outside.

747
00:56:33.458 --> 00:56:35.708
If you are wondering what we are doing here

748
00:56:35.791 --> 00:56:38.041
or why I invited this man...

749
00:56:38.125 --> 00:56:39.625
I wonder both.

750
00:56:39.708 --> 00:56:41.416
Colonel Jones. At your service.

751
00:56:41.500 --> 00:56:42.375
This is Abingdon.

752
00:56:42.458 --> 00:56:46.166
an old Bomber Command base
of the RAF. now closed

753
00:56:46.250 --> 00:56:49.375
and used as a training track
for helicopter pilots.

754
00:56:49.458 --> 00:56:50.916
I grew up with the colonel.

755
00:56:51.000 --> 00:56:52.875
I still sweep my parents' entrance

756
00:56:52.958 --> 00:56:54.583
and it has been declared to me twice.

757
00:56:54.666 --> 00:56:55.625
- Three.
- It doesn't matter.

758
00:56:55.708 --> 00:56:59.041
We need someone
coordinate operations.

759
00:56:59.125 --> 00:57:00.166
is not informed

760
00:57:00.250 --> 00:57:02.916
and has left
only to staff you trust.

761
00:57:03.000 --> 00:57:06.125
It is not a foolproof plan.
but something is something.

762
00:57:06.208 --> 00:57:07.083
Thank you. colonel.

763
00:57:08.958 --> 00:57:10.166
After today.

764
00:57:10.250 --> 00:57:13.333
It is clear that Crown
He planned it from the beginning.

765
00:57:14.291 --> 00:57:16.000
He placed the hard drive in Bajwa.

766
00:57:16.083 --> 00:57:18.583
I knew that the Emiratis
they would share it with MI6

767
00:57:18.666 --> 00:57:21.250
and that you would recognize the PMN plan.

768
00:57:23.250 --> 00:57:25.583
He also knew how MI6 would respond.

769
00:57:25.666 --> 00:57:28.541
I knew about the meeting and where it would be.

770
00:57:28.625 --> 00:57:31.125
He knew everything because he planned it.

771
00:57:31.208 --> 00:57:32.833
How do we find it?

772
00:57:32.916 --> 00:57:36.125
-Who shot us in the cathedral?
- Two bodies have been identified.

773
00:57:36.208 --> 00:57:38.125
And they were not from the PMN.

774
00:57:38.208 --> 00:57:39.666
Not even close.

775
00:57:39.750 --> 00:57:43.500
They had ties to a group
Russian paramilitary called Otomstits.

776
00:57:44.291 --> 00:57:45.583
It was formed in the 80s.

777
00:57:45.666 --> 00:57:47.875
but it was removed in the mid-2000s.

778
00:57:49.000 --> 00:57:49.875
Starling.

779
00:57:51.250 --> 00:57:52.416
Fuck.

780
00:57:53.958 --> 00:57:56.083
Crown is reactivating terrorist groups.

781
00:57:56.166 --> 00:57:57.000
No.

782
00:57:58.333 --> 00:58:01.291
It is reactivating terrorist groups
that Starling dismantled.

783
00:58:01.375 --> 00:58:02.708
What do you want?

784
00:58:02.791 --> 00:58:05.083
- Demonstrate something.
- Prove something?

785
00:58:05.166 --> 00:58:06.333
Demonstrate something key.

786
00:58:07.000 --> 00:58:09.416
What. if not
for shows like Starling.

787
00:58:09.500 --> 00:58:12.125
These terrorist groups could attack

788
00:58:12.208 --> 00:58:14.625
