789
00:58:16.083 --> 00:58:19.791
Because that's what happens
when you leave the doors open.

790
00:58:21.125 --> 00:58:23.791
That's why Nigel was in Dubai.
to kill Crown.

791
00:58:23.875 --> 00:58:25.583
No. he was in Dubai for me.

792
00:58:25.666 --> 00:58:27.375
What was your objective?

793
00:58:27.458 --> 00:58:30.000
had infiltrated
in the Crown operation

794
00:58:30.083 --> 00:58:33.250
to get information
and that we could stop it.

795
00:58:34.041 --> 00:58:35.541
I was trying to warn you.

796
00:58:35.625 --> 00:58:37.916
Given what happened today.

797
00:58:38.000 --> 00:58:39.708
I'd say Crown was trying to kill you.

798
00:58:40.583 --> 00:58:41.666
I wish I had done it.

799
00:58:41.750 --> 00:58:42.875
Well. you know what?

800
00:58:43.375 --> 00:58:45.500
Now you're the director of the fucking CIA.

801
00:58:45.583 --> 00:58:48.041
Let's see where that son of a bitch is coming from.

802
00:58:48.125 --> 00:58:49.791
You are the director of the CIA.

803
00:58:51.833 --> 00:58:53.500
It's more than I planned.

804
00:58:53.583 --> 00:58:56.541
- That?
- Wright got into the car and changed plans.

805
00:58:57.250 --> 00:58:59.291
He saw an opportunity.

806
00:58:59.375 --> 00:59:02.250
You said it yourself:
our agency was going to arrest him.

807
00:59:02.333 --> 00:59:04.708
But what if another director released him?

808
00:59:06.291 --> 00:59:08.208
- He knows I would kill him.
- No.

809
00:59:08.291 --> 00:59:10.333
I would have a plan against that.

810
00:59:10.416 --> 00:59:12.958
Sorry to interrupt. We have a problem.

811
00:59:14.791 --> 00:59:16.208
He says it's for James Greer.

812
00:59:17.833 --> 00:59:19.666
How the hell did he find us?

813
00:59:21.958 --> 00:59:22.791
Review it.

814
00:59:37.791 --> 00:59:38.625
Clean!

815
00:59:40.166 --> 00:59:43.166
{\an8}UBER EATS
DISTRIBUTION

816
00:59:46.708 --> 00:59:49.083
YOU ARE NOT THE FIRST
GREAT TRAITOR OF NORTH AMERICA

817
00:59:53.500 --> 00:59:54.541
I know where it is.

818
01:00:28.625 --> 01:00:29.500
Stay tuned.

819
01:00:30.333 --> 01:00:31.208
It will appear.

820
01:00:38.458 --> 01:00:39.291
I see it.

821
01:00:53.375 --> 01:00:55.250
What do you want?

822
01:00:57.583 --> 01:01:00.166
Know? As they say.

823
01:01:00.250 --> 01:01:02.500
They brought land from Virginia

824
01:01:02.583 --> 01:01:06.166
so that your virtuous hero
never set foot on British soil again.

825
01:01:06.750 --> 01:01:09.250
It's incredible what is done for honor.

826
01:01:10.041 --> 01:01:11.791
Well. or for appearances.

827
01:01:12.875 --> 01:01:13.875
Please...

828
01:01:15.041 --> 01:01:17.541
You know what happens when you take that out.

829
01:01:19.833 --> 01:01:21.458
Today there will be no heroic deeds.

830
01:01:21.541 --> 01:01:24.916
Neither on your part nor on that of the trafficker
of weapons of that queue.

831
01:01:25.000 --> 01:01:25.833
Fuck.

832
01:01:25.916 --> 01:01:27.958
Not even on the part of the child prodigy.

833
01:01:28.541 --> 01:01:30.583
which is there with Blonde Ambition.

834
01:01:31.083 --> 01:01:34.708
Sincerely. Jim.
I have my doubts about him.

835
01:01:34.791 --> 01:01:36.250
What do you want?

836
01:01:36.833 --> 01:01:37.958
You know what I want:

837
01:01:38.708 --> 01:01:39.750
know what you know.

838
01:01:41.291 --> 01:01:43.125
You knew Nigel had betrayed us.

839
01:01:43.833 --> 01:01:45.625
He gathered information to expose us.

840
01:01:45.708 --> 01:01:48.750
I knew that our dog
He had gotten off the fucking leash.

841
01:01:48.833 --> 01:01:50.958
You were going to use that information.
against my men.

842
01:01:51.625 --> 01:01:52.458
Your men.

843
01:01:52.541 --> 01:01:56.791
Who fought your covert wars
to keep your country safe.

844
01:01:56.875 --> 01:01:58.791
You just have to take down one man.

845
01:01:59.833 --> 01:02:01.708
Do you think you are the one who should do it?

846
01:02:03.125 --> 01:02:05.958
Because it's up to you
Whom the ghosts haunt.

847
01:02:06.041 --> 01:02:07.416
Son of a bitch.

848
01:02:07.500 --> 01:02:08.458
Stay still!

849
01:02:19.666 --> 01:02:21.083
Without hesitation.

850
01:02:22.208 --> 01:02:23.041
Do you remember?

851
01:02:25.041 --> 01:02:26.750
What do you want?

852
01:02:26.833 --> 01:02:28.083
May you go home.

853
01:02:29.000 --> 01:02:31.708
May you continue the great work
that you started years ago.

854
01:02:31.791 --> 01:02:33.333
before the change of power.

855
01:02:33.416 --> 01:02:37.125
Before to your country
You will suddenly feel remorse.

856
01:02:39.208 --> 01:02:42.166
We maintained world balance.

857
01:02:42.750 --> 01:02:47.000
I want you to give my men. your men.
the opportunity to do it again.

858
01:02:48.375 --> 01:02:51.625
and you can start
giving me back what Nigel stole from me.

859
01:02:52.666 --> 01:02:54.166
I don't know what you're talking about.

860
01:02:55.416 --> 01:02:58.208
Jim. the longer we wait.
more people will die.

861
01:02:58.291 --> 01:02:59.250
I don't have anything.

862
01:02:59.958 --> 01:03:00.875
God...

863
01:03:00.958 --> 01:03:01.958
He doesn't have it.

864
01:03:03.166 --> 01:03:04.000
I have it.

865
01:03:06.333 --> 01:03:07.333
Wow. look.

866
01:03:10.125 --> 01:03:11.833
Give it back to me. please.

867
01:03:11.916 --> 01:03:14.208
Do you really believe
What would I wear something like that?

868
01:03:14.791 --> 01:03:16.666
Don't tell me you gave it to MI6.

869
01:03:18.166 --> 01:03:20.000
With what happened to Nigel?

870
01:03:20.083 --> 01:03:21.708
How could I trust MI6?

871
01:03:24.541 --> 01:03:26.291
Your boy is going to be worth it in the end.

872
01:03:32.041 --> 01:03:33.166
You didn't know?

873
01:03:33.708 --> 01:03:35.250
Marvelous.

874
01:03:36.583 --> 01:03:37.500
Where is?

875
01:03:38.125 --> 01:03:39.125
I left him in Dubai.

876
01:03:43.458 --> 01:03:45.583
Okay. then to Dubai.

877
01:03:46.333 --> 01:03:48.041
Where do you want me to take it?

878
01:03:48.625 --> 01:03:52.000
I think today it has become very clear:
I will find you.

879
01:03:56.958 --> 01:03:58.166
What the hell was he talking about?

880
01:03:58.250 --> 01:04:00.250
Did Nigel give you something?
and you haven't told me?

881
01:04:00.333 --> 01:04:01.625
- No. I lied.
- That?

882
01:04:01.708 --> 01:04:03.250
I have gained time.

883
01:04:03.333 --> 01:04:05.458
I promise you it didn't give me
nothing more than this.

884
01:04:05.541 --> 01:04:07.000
Review it. There is nothing.

885
01:04:07.583 --> 01:04:10.375
- There will be something.
- Crown has said he saw it with his eyes.

886
01:04:10.458 --> 01:04:12.541
That's why Nigel gave it to me.

887
01:04:12.625 --> 01:04:15.583
If you thought he was going to give me something.
Crown too.

888
01:04:15.666 --> 01:04:18.041
Nigel gave me that because he knew
that Crown was watching us.

889
01:04:18.125 --> 01:04:19.875
So what are we looking for?

890
01:04:19.958 --> 01:04:21.833
When Nigel's agents were killed

891
01:04:21.916 --> 01:04:24.208
Was there any transmission?
Any communication?

892
01:04:24.291 --> 01:04:25.458
- No idea.
- Shit.

893
01:04:25.541 --> 01:04:27.375
- I wasn't aware.
- There had to be.

894
01:04:28.250 --> 01:04:30.750
The rush to find me.
the death of those men...

895
01:04:30.833 --> 01:04:33.958
The good thing is that we have
24 hours to find it.

896
01:04:34.041 --> 01:04:38.083
Depending on how far they went.
They could access anything:

897
01:04:38.166 --> 01:04:40.833
files. plans. finances...

898
01:04:40.916 --> 01:04:44.000
Whatever it was.
I would leave it to someone I trusted.

899
01:04:45.541 --> 01:04:47.250
Can you sneak us into his MI6 office?

900
01:04:47.875 --> 01:04:48.875
MI6?

901
01:04:49.875 --> 01:04:51.708
How could he trust them?

902
01:05:10.375 --> 01:05:11.833
Damn. thank goodness.

903
01:05:11.916 --> 01:05:14.041
- Hello. Arthur.
- I was worried.

904
01:05:14.125 --> 01:05:18.000
Alright. He is traveling. Don't worry.

905
01:05:18.083 --> 01:05:20.625
He? I don't give a damn about your father.

906
01:05:21.708 --> 01:05:24.625
If I am in a situation without living
It's for the 400 pounds he owes me.

907
01:05:24.708 --> 01:05:27.583
That's why I came. to pay your bill.
Do you have the key?

908
01:05:28.791 --> 01:05:31.166
Okay. Tell him we miss him.

909
01:05:32.541 --> 01:05:33.541
I will do that.

910
01:05:42.333 --> 01:05:44.458
So this is what awaits me.

911
01:05:52.875 --> 01:05:54.416
Doesn't anyone know about this apartment?

912
01:05:55.208 --> 01:05:56.208
No.

913
01:05:56.958 --> 01:05:58.541
Except his daughter. of course.

914
01:05:59.041 --> 01:06:01.583
When you can't get close. fake it.

915
01:06:15.416 --> 01:06:16.333
What a fabric.

916
01:06:17.000 --> 01:06:18.666
Does that thing still work?

917
01:06:19.333 --> 01:06:21.791
It predates the internet.
No search engines.

918
01:06:23.375 --> 01:06:24.375
Very clever.

919
01:06:24.875 --> 01:06:26.625
Yes. So don't make fun.

920
01:06:32.208 --> 01:06:34.125
- That?
- I kept photos.

921
01:06:34.958 --> 01:06:36.125
And I saw them blur.

922
01:06:37.708 --> 01:06:40.625
I have always thought
What if I knew someone...

923
01:06:42.708 --> 01:06:46.791
...I would have to keep it
as far as possible from this world.

924
01:06:48.291 --> 01:06:49.416
And how has it been for you?

925
01:06:49.500 --> 01:06:51.166
Very well thank you. And you?

926
01:06:51.250 --> 01:06:52.250
Equal.

927
01:06:52.833 --> 01:06:54.666
I'm sure they're together now.

928
01:06:54.750 --> 01:06:56.750
Well he has been lucky.

929
01:06:56.833 --> 01:06:57.833
Not her.

930
01:07:00.750 --> 01:07:02.958
Nothing. No emails or messages.

931
01:07:03.625 --> 01:07:06.875
And the last opened files
They are from a week before Dubai.

932
01:07:06.958 --> 01:07:09.666
- Any open website? Programs. chats?
- No.

933
01:07:09.750 --> 01:07:10.750
Chats?

934
01:07:11.583 --> 01:07:12.666
Do you still use AOL?

935
01:07:13.333 --> 01:07:14.333
Maybe.

936
01:07:14.916 --> 01:07:17.250
- Do you mind if...?
- Forward.

937
01:07:19.625 --> 01:07:22.541
Luck. If your apartment seems like a disaster to you.
wait until you see his album.

938
01:07:22.625 --> 01:07:23.708
My mother.

939
01:07:26.250 --> 01:07:27.625
It wouldn't make sense.

940
01:07:27.708 --> 01:07:30.750
Sending something would be too risky.

941
01:07:30.833 --> 01:07:32.625
It would be visible to everyone.

942
01:07:32.708 --> 01:07:35.333
Why would it be risky
What if no one knows it's here?

943
01:07:37.166 --> 01:07:38.166
God!

944
01:07:38.875 --> 01:07:39.750
What's that?

945
01:07:42.625 --> 01:07:46.041
Hey. I'll keep using AOL.
but even I have stopped using Torrents.

946
01:07:47.625 --> 01:07:49.833
And aren't you ashamed to say that out loud?

947
01:07:49.916 --> 01:07:51.708
- "Torrents"?
- Yes. Both things.

948
01:07:51.791 --> 01:07:53.708
- Didn't you go to uni?
- No.

949
01:07:53.791 --> 01:07:55.791
- They are like a music website.
- Thank you.

950
01:07:55.875 --> 01:07:58.625
- For downloads. Like Napster.
- I get it.

951
01:07:58.708 --> 01:08:00.750
You play chess online.

952
01:08:00.833 --> 01:08:02.250
Who's making fun now?

953
01:08:03.583 --> 01:08:06.750
It's not that. It is any website that has...

954
01:08:10.375 --> 01:08:11.500
With an external server.

955
01:08:11.583 --> 01:08:12.875
PROCESSES

956
01:08:17.083 --> 01:08:18.458
What a bastard.

957
01:08:18.541 --> 01:08:21.375
Damn. you were right. Nothing went up.

958
01:08:21.958 --> 01:08:23.916
I monitored the live broadcasts.

959
01:08:24.000 --> 01:08:25.000
From where?

960
01:08:38.791 --> 01:08:39.625
Hello!

961
01:08:40.333 --> 01:08:42.708
- No. don't answer like that.
<i>- Jack.</i>

962
01:08:42.791 --> 01:08:44.916
Hey. I need your help.

963
01:08:45.000 --> 01:08:47.416
I want you to trace
the origin of a network connection.

964
01:08:47.500 --> 01:08:48.791
<i>I'm sending it to you.</i>

965
01:08:51.708 --> 01:08:52.958
Okay. Good.

966
01:08:53.041 --> 01:08:55.250
<i>- You are now a civilian.</i>
- Yes.

967
01:08:55.333 --> 01:08:59.875
And you swore a long oath
and detailed to protect civilians. me.

968
01:08:59.958 --> 01:09:02.166
so that's your job.

969
01:09:03.125 --> 01:09:05.166
That is if they don't fire me.

970
01:09:05.250 --> 01:09:06.750
<i>- How do you say?</i>
- Nothing.

971
01:09:12.666 --> 01:09:14.125
I would like Madonna.

972
01:09:15.708 --> 01:09:17.416
<i>Okay. I'm ready.</i>

973
01:09:19.750 --> 01:09:20.958
"The Blonde Ambition."

974
01:09:22.666 --> 01:09:23.666
<i>Jack?</i>

975
01:09:25.875 --> 01:09:29.208
In Trafalgar Square.
Crown called you "Blonde Ambition."

976
01:09:31.208 --> 01:09:32.208
He's been here.

977
01:09:33.583 --> 01:09:35.916
Are you sure no one else
Do you know about this floor?

978
01:09:36.000 --> 01:09:37.000
Yes.

979
01:09:39.000 --> 01:09:40.250
Not even Spear?

980
01:10:02.375 --> 01:10:03.833
Our options are terrible.

981
01:10:05.541 --> 01:10:08.750
If we do not find the information.
They will attack again.

982
01:10:09.333 --> 01:10:10.416
What if we find her?

983
01:10:11.000 --> 01:10:13.666
The director of the CIA
negotiates with a terrorist.

984
01:10:14.958 --> 01:10:17.166
The president wouldn't be very happy.

985
01:10:18.750 --> 01:10:20.166
The third option is to kill him.

986
01:10:21.916 --> 01:10:23.625
It's the only way to stop this.

987
01:10:25.916 --> 01:10:28.125
Mike. I appreciate you being here.

988
01:10:30.583 --> 01:10:31.583
but you don't have to.

989
01:10:32.500 --> 01:10:33.500
I already know.

990
01:10:36.083 --> 01:10:37.041
It's curious.

991
01:10:37.708 --> 01:10:39.750
You and Jack are always arguing

992
01:10:39.833 --> 01:10:41.250
about what is right and wrong.

993
01:10:42.375 --> 01:10:45.208
You refuse to accept fucking reality.

994
01:10:45.708 --> 01:10:48.166
I assumed it a long time ago.

995
01:10:49.791 --> 01:10:51.041
What reality?

996
01:10:52.708 --> 01:10:53.708
That the three of us are

997
01:10:55.041 --> 01:10:56.541
the only family we will have.

998
01:10:57.708 --> 01:10:59.000
When you understand that.

999
01:11:00.000 --> 01:11:02.125
You know just where you should be.

1000
01:11:11.208 --> 01:11:12.833
The wife. precisely.

1001
01:11:13.708 --> 01:11:15.083
Hello. Do you have anything?

1002
01:11:17.041 --> 01:11:19.458
Of course. Wait.

1003
01:11:20.083 --> 01:11:21.583
We already have another option.

1004
01:11:22.666 --> 01:11:25.000
Jack. Where the hell are you?

1005
01:11:26.250 --> 01:11:27.833
With Ryan. following a lead.

1006
01:11:27.916 --> 01:11:30.208
A clue? What kind of track?

1007
01:11:30.791 --> 01:11:33.958
He said he could decipher
the record that Nigel gave him.

1008
01:11:34.041 --> 01:11:36.583
so I brought it to the Flagon.

1009
01:11:37.833 --> 01:11:40.458
<i>- Do you know him?</i>
- Your apartment. yes. AND?

1010
01:11:41.875 --> 01:11:43.500
<i>Was there something there?</i>

1011
01:11:44.791 --> 01:11:47.000
No. Nothing useful.

1012
01:11:48.666 --> 01:11:51.541
I didn't have a hard drive. It was a server.

1013
01:11:52.333 --> 01:11:54.500
A server? What server?

1014
01:11:55.083 --> 01:11:58.833
You said you needed Nigel to give you
information to take down Crown.

1015
01:11:58.916 --> 01:12:01.375
What if he found the origin
of the entire Crown operation

1016
01:12:01.458 --> 01:12:04.083
and I was going to transmit it
that night from Dubai?

1017
01:12:04.666 --> 01:12:05.875
Dubai...

1018
01:12:05.958 --> 01:12:08.083
Crown stopped him before he did it.

1019
01:12:08.166 --> 01:12:10.416
<i>God. And what plan do you have?</i>

1020
01:12:12.000 --> 01:12:13.166
Try again.

1021
01:12:29.208 --> 01:12:30.416
Good. Here we go.

1022
01:12:30.500 --> 01:12:31.916
This is not going to work.

1023
01:12:32.416 --> 01:12:33.916
You don't attract attention.

1024
01:12:44.541 --> 01:12:46.291
- They leave.
<i>- Who?</i>

1025
01:12:46.375 --> 01:12:48.833
Greer and November. They return home.

1026
01:12:48.916 --> 01:12:50.083
And Ryan?

1027
01:12:50.166 --> 01:12:52.166
<i>He has not attended the meeting point.</i>

1028
01:12:52.250 --> 01:12:54.750
<i>Has he already gone to retrieve the package?</i>

1029
01:12:54.833 --> 01:12:56.333
We would know.

1030
01:13:02.416 --> 01:13:03.500
Follow Greer.

1031
01:13:27.916 --> 01:13:28.750
Okay...

1032
01:13:29.791 --> 01:13:31.458
Were you expecting an escort?

1033
01:13:31.541 --> 01:13:34.791
No. it's just the first surprise today.

1034
01:13:35.625 --> 01:13:37.041
Well it won't be the last.

1035
01:13:43.041 --> 01:13:45.500
They will arrive in less than 20 minutes.

1036
01:13:45.583 --> 01:13:46.750
<i>Roger. sir.</i>

1037
01:13:47.250 --> 01:13:49.666
By the way. you're still on duty.

1038
01:13:49.750 --> 01:13:52.958
Do you mean today
or are you talking about something permanent?

1039
01:13:53.041 --> 01:13:54.708
Depending on how today turns out.

1040
01:13:55.416 --> 01:13:56.750
Okay. Brilliant.

1041
01:14:00.500 --> 01:14:02.166
I don't even look like him.

1042
01:14:42.125 --> 01:14:43.583
Ryan and Marlow on the move.

1043
01:14:45.375 --> 01:14:46.375
Say "potato."

1044
01:14:46.458 --> 01:14:47.458
No.

1045
01:14:47.541 --> 01:14:50.833
Okay. Today is going to be a very long day.

1046
01:14:57.500 --> 01:14:59.000
501st SUPPORT SQUADRON

1047
01:14:59.083 --> 01:15:01.041
US AIR FORCE

1048
01:15:21.416 --> 01:15:24.333
Friends. some instructions
about security.

